              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Abilità Elementale</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Infligge 3 </span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">DAN da Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/248396191/2efa0cba0a06e11bae77666bb6beb952_1334255376323326641.png",
                "id": "talent85527",
                "key": "Attacco gelante",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Attacco gelante"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Tripudio Elementale</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Infligge 1 </span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">DAN da Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">, crea una </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Stalattite</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Stalattite</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Stato di combattimento</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Dopo aver cambiato personaggio:</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> infliggi 2 </span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">DAN da Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.<br></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Utilizzi: 3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/03/248396191/8c97595e1862a7f3d9d0b707c3143148_1294762902157825327.png",
                "id": "talent84392",
                "key": "Valzer glaciale",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Valzer glaciale"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Applica Cryo e può innescare le seguenti reazioni elementali:<br></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">]</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Fusione</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DAN inflitti +2.<br></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">] Superconduzione</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DAN inflitti +1, infligge 1 DAN da perforazione a tutti i personaggi nemici tranne al bersaglio.<br></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">] Congelamento</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DAN inflitti +1, impedisce al bersaglio di eseguire azioni durante il turno corrente (può essere rimosso in anticipo se riceve danni fisici o da Pyro, nel caso subisce DAN +2).</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/05/35428890/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_8249498161234896063.png",
                "id": "talent35826",
                "key": "DAN da Cryo",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "DAN da Cryo"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">DAN fisici</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">I DAN fisici non applicano alcun elemento né innescano reazioni elementali.</span><br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Utilizzi</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Dopo che l'effetto di questa carta è stato innescato, viene consumato 1 </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Utilizzo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.<br>Quando tutti gli </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Utilizzi </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">saranno stati consumati, la carta verrà eliminata.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1736824361030426636.png",
